{"about_the_game":"Experience a world unlike any other as you take on the role of a tiny robot on a mission to bring light back to a darkened planet. In this innovative puzzle-platformer, you'll use the incredible mechanic of manipulating light and shadow to change your surroundings, solve intricate puzzles, and collect shards to resurrect a fallen star.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/590850/extras/Copy_of_rooftop1.gif?t=1726172936\" /><br><br>As you explore the beautifully stylized world of Night Lights, you'll encounter a variety of challenges that will test your problem-solving skills. From navigating complex platforms to finding the portable light bulb, you'll need to use all of your wits to progress through the game's 45 levels, each with its own unique set of puzzles and solutions.<br><br>But you won't be alone in your quest for light. With the ability to collect crystals and activate different tools and light sources, you'll have the tools you need to overcome any obstacle. So gather your courage and join the adventure of a lifetime as you embark on a journey to bring light back to the world in Night Lights.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"RUN BOT RUN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/590850/92a976966ddcf9b03da762fcc9ae3a094abc25d9.jpg"},{"name":"DOUBLE-JUMP","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/590850/cb9faea29982e0a75faa273b595b58aba1aeb1d6.jpg"},{"name":"LET THERE BE LIGHT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/590850/771e0136567a33d907165513f79a7427afc0fbd7.jpg"},{"name":"DASHING","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/590850/af51cc0cc0bd267db1be20b08d0b6cdff667c71a.jpg"},{"name":"CUT!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/590850/e1a41a7d5c0fdaa9ae17f035454e91e5b31b9804.jpg"},{"n